	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=37105><span id= >KingKong</span></a><br><span id=notbold>34 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.38]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Damage cap works like this:<br><br>lvl 1 to 10 your weapon is capped at 10 damage (10x2=20 +1 = 21)<br>at lvl 10 to 20 your weapon damage is capped at 14 (14x2=28 +1=29)<br>and after lvl 20 damage cap is lifted...HOORAY! <br><br>As far as the epic it is a 2HS (A BAD ASS) As far as which is best used, I think we have mostly alot of 1HB and 2HS that are SK only.&nbsp;&nbsp;Not sure, but it is always best to keep them all maxed.  It will be hard untill lvl 20 to max more than 2.  Basically you should use what ever best weapons you have available to you.  Look into getting a dark reaver, Cheap 2HS with great Dmg.  A little slow.  get a Axe of the Iron back for cheap (they sell for like 20pp on Sol Ro) and use it till lvl 20 then use the dark reaver.  Those 2 weaps are great if you dont have allota cash and will see you to lvl 30 easy.<br><br>As far as your str.  Str as all stats have a minute affect.  You wont see a differance in between a 90str and a 110 str.  <br>Hope this helped Dark brother, may you cause pain and suffering to those around you.<br><br>Syphun Iksar SK on SolRo</p>&nbsp;<br>Feel free to rate my posts<br>Be honest I can take it...<br><br>I intend to live forever - so far, so good</td></td></tr>
